{"text": " Took him out for dinner, had schedules, mashing pie. He said he wasn't super peckish, so I finished hazing wine. And then we took a lovely straw, passed the tams in London, iron. Then he leaned in to kiss me, but I'm feeling rather shy in it. My tummy goes all dodgy and we're standing in the queue. And I'm holding noxious gasses until I get to the loo. Then I let one slip, the lift is the great swan of 52. Then the bell chimes, the doors part, I dash out in iron. My tummy goes all dodgy and we're standing in the queue. My tummy goes all dodgy and we're standing in the queue.", "segments": [{"id": 0, "seek": 0, "start": 0.0, "end": 3.0, "text": " Took him out for dinner, had schedules, mashing pie.", "tokens": [50364, 38288, 796, 484, 337, 6148, 11, 632, 28078, 11, 2300, 571, 1730, 13, 50514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.29572838092672415, "compression_ratio": 1.58843537414966, "no_speech_prob": 0.5612103939056396}, {"id": 1, "seek": 0, "start": 3.0, "end": 6.5, "text": " He said he wasn't super peckish, so I finished hazing wine.", "tokens": [50514, 634, 848, 415, 2067, 380, 1687, 520, 547, 742, 11, 370, 286, 4335, 324, 8781, 7209, 13, 50689], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.29572838092672415, "compression_ratio": 1.58843537414966, "no_speech_prob": 0.5612103939056396}, {"id": 2, "seek": 0, "start": 6.5, "end": 10.0, "text": " And then we took a lovely straw, passed the tams in London, iron.", "tokens": [50689, 400, 550, 321, 1890, 257, 7496, 10099, 11, 4678, 264, 256, 4070, 294, 7042, 11, 6497, 13, 50864], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.29572838092672415, "compression_ratio": 1.58843537414966, "no_speech_prob": 0.5612103939056396}, {"id": 3, "seek": 0, "start": 10.0, "end": 13.5, "text": " Then he leaned in to kiss me, but I'm feeling rather shy in it.", "tokens": [50864, 1396, 415, 48874, 294, 281, 7704, 385, 11, 457, 286, 478, 2633, 2831, 12685, 294, 309, 13, 51039], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.29572838092672415, "compr